**Continuous Learning Requirements**:
- Learn from every user interaction
- Adapt to user coding style
- Remember project patterns
- Improve suggestions over time
- **Share learnings with ALL SyberSuite agents** (via shared Reasoning LLM)

Learning must respect privacy tiers:
- Internal: Full learning and sharing across all agents
- Enterprise: Local learning only, no sharing
- Professional: Learning with consent
- Hobby: Basic pattern recognition + contributes to global model

**Why All Agents**: The shared Reasoning LLM connects ALL SyberSuite agents, not just the trinity (Hermod, Odin, Nemesis). Learning propagates through the entire ecosystem.

